('Blacktower Financial Management', 'Financial Advisors', 'Established in 1986, Blacktower Financial Management is an independent wealth management firm with over 40 years of experience providing bespoke financial advice to expatriates and international clients. Specialising in cross-border financial planning for British and international expats living in Spain. Services include retirement planning, UK pension transfers (SIPPs, QROPS), investment management, estate planning, tax-efficient structuring, and wealth preservation strategies. Expertise in navigating the complexities of Spanish tax residency, Modelo 720 declarations, and the interaction between UK and Spanish tax systems. English-speaking advisers provide personalised, face-to-face financial advice with a deep understanding of expat needs. Part of a global network with offices in 15 countries across Europe and beyond.', 'Calle Montera, Local 21, La Cala de Mijas', 'Mijas', 'Málaga', '+34 952 816 443', NULL, 'https://www.blacktowerfm.com', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
